Package accounts

Class LibrarianRow

java.lang.Object
accounts.LibrarianRow
public class LibrarianRow
extends java.lang.Object
The LibrarianRow class contains the data of the Librarian table in the MySQL database. When the viewAllLibrariansWindowReport() method of the ViewAllLibrariansController class and the init() method of the MyController class is called, this LibrarianRow object will be used to display data from the table.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Tim Lai
